io.prometheus.client

Annotation Type Register


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Register

    Register Metric and their derivatives with the Prometheus registrar across all runtime libraries and their dependencies.

    The purpose of this runtime annotation is to provide a common fragment to search for across an entire server's classpath for metrics to export. Due to nuances in the underlying Java Virtual Machine implementations, not every class referenced in an application's transitive closure will be loaded. This can prevent telemetry from being found and registered! Each Metric decorated with Metric will be found and registered for exposition across all libraries your server depends on.

    Author:
    matt.proud@gmail.com (Matt T. Proud)
